g.title: incoming_vote_result
g.text: Takes a mapping of voters to
a result indicating whether the vote
is pending (i.e. neither a quorum of
yes/no has been reached), won (a quorum
of yes has been reached), or lost (a
quorum of no has been reached).

g.text: 而且自己不是leader 且commit比自己的大
